**CPU Andie Sprite**
   When green flag is clicked
      Say "Hello!" for 2 seconds
      Wait 1 second
      Say "You think you can beat me" for 2 seconds
      Wait 1 second
      Say "Ready?" for 1.5 seconds
      Wait 0.75 seconds
      Say "3" for 0.75 seconds
      Wait 0.5 seconds
      Say "2" for 0.75 seconds
      Wait 0.5 seconds
      Say "1" for 0.75 seconds
      Wait 0.5 seconds
      Say "GO!" for 0.9 seconds
      Broadcast "go"
      
   When green flag is clicked
      Set CPU score to 0
      
   When green flag is clicked
      Show sprite
      
   When I recieve go
      Loop forever
         Wait 1.5 to 3.6 seconds
         Add 1 point to CPU score
         
   When I recieve go
      Loop forever
         Wait 1 second
         Go to next costume
         
   When I recieve "message 1"
      Hide sprite
      
   When I recieve "message 2"
      Hide sprite
      
   
**Basketball Sprite**
   When green flag is clicked
      Go to coordinates (-199,-142)
      
   When I recieve "go"
      Show sprite
      
   When I recieve "go"
      Loop forever
         Point the sprite toward the mouse pointer
         Move 7 steps
         
   When I recieve "go"
      Loop forever
         If touching Sprite 2
            Go to coordinate (-199, -142)
   
   When I recieve "message 1"
      Hide sprite
      
   When I recieve "message 2"
      Hide sprite
      
   
**Sprite 1, Top of Hoop**
   When green flag is clicked
      Loop forever
         Show sprite
   
   When green flag is clicked
      Set "User Score" to 0
      Loop forever
         If touching "basketball"
            Add 1 to "Your Score"
            Wait 1 second
            
    When I recieve "message 1"
      Loop forever
         Hide sprite
    
    When I recieve "message 2"
      Loop forever
         Hide sprite
         
**Sprite 2, Bottom of the Hoop**
   When green flag is clicked
      Loop forever
         Go to coordinates (35, 104)
   
   When green flag is clicked
      Loop forever
         Show
   
   When I recieve "message 1"
      Hide sprite
    
    When I revieve "message 2"
      Hide sprite
